---
title: Pork Sausage over Autumn Pilaf drizzled with a Creamy Lemon Pepper Sauce
description: This hearty, cozy pilaf delivers ultimate autumnal vibes. It stars bulgur wheat, an ancient grain we love for its chewy texture and earthy, nutty flavor. The grain’s simmered with stock, smoky-warm spices, and aromatic thyme, then tossed with roasted parsnip, apple, and onion. It’s all topped with slices of of juicy pork sausage for rich, savory notes, then drizzled with a creamy lemon sauce for refreshing brightness.
